summary: This mod add a little outpost near Dawnstar
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://s17.postimage.org/4crf69633/manny_outpost.png[/img][/center]

[center][img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/images/13199-2-1332099456.jpg[/img][/center]

* OVERVIEW *
This mod add a little outpost near Dawnstar (west side coast).

* INSTALLATION *
Place the ESP into data path and activate it by the menu launcher (option \"data files\")
Run the game and enjoy

* UNINSTALLATION *
Disable the file by the menu launcher and delete it.

* COMPATIBILITY *
This mod will be compatible with any mods installed. It just add more objects and lights.

* BUGS *
Please report to me if you find any bug or anomaly.

[center][size=10pt]Check all my mods![/size]
